        <p begin="00:18:21.8" end="00:18:25.9" tts:direction="ltr">Enter and you can see here it went back to
<br/>625.</p>
        <p begin="00:18:25.9" end="00:18:28.9" tts:direction="ltr">Super powerful, really important</p>
        <p begin="00:18:28.9" end="00:18:31.10" tts:direction="ltr">to understand that we can manipulate
<br/>database data.</p>
        <p begin="00:18:31.10" end="00:18:33.5" tts:direction="ltr">It can insert, update,</p>
        <p begin="00:18:33.5" end="00:18:35.4" tts:direction="ltr">delete records of data.</p>
        <p begin="00:18:35.4" end="00:18:38.3" tts:direction="ltr">Thanks everybody. Take care.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>